reverse proxy is a server placed btw user and backend server
it recieve client req
and forward them to correct backend server
client -> load balancer -> reverse proxy-> backend server
reverse proxy also perform load balancer


| Reverse Proxy                    | Load Balancer                                |
| -------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------- |
| Sits in front of backend servers | Sits in front of multiple servers            |
| Receives and forwards requests   | Distributes traffic                          |
| Can hide backend servers         | Prevents one server from becoming overloaded |
| Can handle TLS and caching       | Performs health checks                       |
| Can route by URL path            | Selects a healthy server                     |


Client requests → Load balancer distributes → Reverse proxy routes → Backend server processes.
